                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s) for kernel 5.14.0-611.42.1.el9_7:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;RHEL-9.7&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;buildcheck&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; buildcheck test fails due to fatal error: iwl-trans.h: No such file or directory (JIRA:RHEL-106032)&lt;/li&gt;
